abstract: Answers to our quiz on economic news.
snippet: Answers to our quiz on economic news.
lead_paragraph: Earlier today we posted our first “EconoQuiz,” a news quiz about economic issues. By about 6 p.m., we had around 760 entries, but not a single person answered all 10 questions correctly. Five different readers tied for the highest score of eight correct answers: Olga, Travis Borton, Ross eisenbrey, brett and bmn.
